title: Yankees clinch playoff spot after 2-year absence, top Boston
text:
> Top News Yankees clinch playoff spot after 2-year absence, top Boston New York Yankees on-deck batter John Ryan Murphy greets Yankees Carlos Beltran after Beltran hit a second-inning, solo home run off Boston Red Sox starting pitcher Rich Hill in a baseball game in New York, Thursday, Oct. 1, 2015. (AP Photo/Kathy Willens)
